<p>Circuits with <strong>many current sources</strong>, few meshes</p></td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td class=3D"confluenceTd">
<p>Works With</p></td>
<td class=3D"confluenceTd">
<p>Any planar circuit (with some tweaks for non-planar)</p></td>
<td class=3D"confluenceTd">
<p>Planar circuits only</p></td>
</tr>
</tbody>
