<tr>
<td class=3D"confluenceTd">
<p><strong>Capacitors</strong></p></td>
<td class=3D"confluenceTd">
<p>1Ceq=3D=E2=88=911Ck\displaystyle \frac{1}{C_{eq}} =3D \sum \frac{1}{C_k}=
</p></td>
<td class=3D"confluenceTd">
<p>Ceq=3D=E2=88=91CkC_{eq} =3D \sum C_k</p></td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td class=3D"confluenceTd">
